1. Url Path Based Routing: Based on the url prefix, route to different backend
2. Redirect : global port redirect, from http to https 
3. MutiSite Hosting: host more than one pool, based on the host name 
4. Session affinity: keep the same user on the same server
5. SSl termination: offloading encrption/decrption for backend 
6. Web Application Firewall
7. Health Probe, logging, Monitoring
